      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING TESFAY (2) has a strong overall record having four wins and 10 places from 18 starts but was out of the money last time when fifth (30.49) over 520m at this track. Solid record at the distance winning two races. Well placed here and can go close with a clear run. NOAKI UNO (1) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth (30.33) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Great chance to atone. IDEA'S MAN (3) is having his first start around this track. Comes here after a last start 4th and beaten 3.5 lengths (20.14) at Capalaba. Strong form has emerged from his last run. One of the better chances. PROFESSOR SAXON (7) hit the frame here last time and looks a chance again.",
